data.description:
Walk to Mockingbird Elementary from this original home that is so excited for your finishing touches. Enter into a large formal living room and dining room with original hardwoods, new windows and plantation shutters.  Galley kitchen with breakfast nook, 3 bed, 2 bath with a 2 car garage. Great flow!  All this house needs is a little TLC. House is being sold As-Is. Seller does not have a survey. This one is priced to sell, so do not wait!
All offers will be reviewed by Monday February 7 at noon. Multiple offers have been received.  Please send proof of funds and all offers to Aimee Elkman.
